<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>일본어 문자 쓰기 수행평가 툴</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700;900&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/xlsx/0.18.5/xlsx.full.min.js"></script>
<style>
:root{
  --bg:#f5f2e8;--card:#fff;
  --green-l:#c8ddb0;--green-d:#5a8a3c;--green-t:#4a7a32;
  --text:#2d2d2d;--text-l:#666;--border:#d0c9b0;
  --red:#c0392b;--red-bg:#fdf2f0;
  --amber:#d68910;--amber-bg:#fdf8ec;
  --green:#1e8449;--green-bg:#edfaf3;
  --sh:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
body{font-family:"Noto Sans KR",sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);min-height:100vh;}

.screen{display:none;}
.screen.active{display:flex;flex-direction:column;min-height:100vh;}

/* ── 헤더 ── */
.hdr{background:var(--green-d);color:#fff;padding:0 20px;height:50px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:200;}
.hdr .brand{font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-0.3px;flex:1;min-width:0;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;}
.hdr .step{margin-left:auto;font-size:.68rem;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);letter-spacing:1.2px;text-transform:uppercase;flex-shrink:0;white-space:nowrap;}

/* ── 공통 ── */
.cwrap{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:28px 20px;gap:18px;}
.card{background:var(--card);border-radius:16px;box-shadow:var(--sh);padding:22px 26px;width:100%;}
.ctitle{font-size:.68rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--text-l);letter-spacing:1.4px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;}
.ctitle::before{content:"";width:3px;height:12px;background:var(--green-d);border-radius:2px;display:inline-block;}

.btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:5px;padding:9px 18px;border:none;border-radius:9px;font-size:.86rem;font-weight:700;font-family:inherit;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;}
.btn-green{background:var(--green-l);color:var(--green-t);}
.btn-green:hover{background:#b0cc98;}
.btn-dark{background:var(--green-d);color:#fff;}
.btn-dark:hover{background:#4a7a32;}
.btn-ol{background:#fff;color:var(--text);border:1.5px solid var(--border);}
.btn-ol:hover{border-color:var(--green-d);color:var(--green-d);}
.btn-full{width:100%;}
.btn:disabled{opacity:.35;cursor:not-allowed;}

/* ══ S1: 문자 선택 ══ */
.hero{text-align:center;}
.hero h1{font-size:2rem;font-weight:900;margin-bottom:6px;color:var(--green-d);}
.hero p{color:var(--text-l);font-size:.86rem;}
.script-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;width:100%;max-width:420px;}
.script-btn{background:#fff;border:2px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:24px 14px;cursor:pointer;text-align:center;transition:all .18s;font-family:inherit;}
.script-btn:hover{border-color:var(--green-d);background:#f0f7e8;transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(0,0,0,.08);}
.script-btn .kana{font-family:"Noto Sans JP",serif;font-size:2.4rem;color:var(--green-d);display:block;margin-bottom:6px;}
.script-btn .lbl{font-size:.92rem;font-weight:700;display:block;}
.script-btn .sub{font-size:.7rem;color:var(--text-l);margin-top:3px;display:block;}

/* ══ S2: 설정 ══ */
.row-btn-group{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:7px;margin-bottom:8px;}
.row-btn{padding:7px 14px;border-radius:20px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);background:#fff;color:var(--text-l);font-size:.8rem;font-weight:600;font-family:inherit;cursor:pointer;transition:all .12s;}
.row-btn:hover{border-color:var(--green-d);color:var(--green-d);}
.row-btn.on{border-color:var(--green-l);background:var(--green-l);color:var(--green-t);}
.info-box{background:#f0f7e8;border-radius:8px;padding:8px 12px;font-size:.74rem;color:var(--text-l);line-height:1.7;margin-top:6px;}
.info-box strong{color:var(--green-d);}

.stepper-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:9px;}
.sitem{background:var(--bg);border-radius:10px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);padding:10px 8px;text-align:center;}
.sitem.sang{border-color:#f5c6c2;background:var(--red-bg);}
.sitem.jung{border-color:#f9e4a0;background:var(--amber-bg);}
.sitem.ha  {border-color:#a9dfbf;background:var(--green-bg);}
.slbl{font-size:.76rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:7px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:4px;}
.dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;}
.dot.sang{background:var(--red);}
.dot.jung{background:var(--amber);}
.dot.ha  {background:var(--green);}
.sctl{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:6px;}
.sbtn{width:24px;height:24px;border-radius:6px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);background:#fff;color:var(--text);font-size:1rem;font-weight:900;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:all .1s;}
.sbtn:hover{background:var(--green-d);color:#fff;border-color:var(--green-d);}
.sval{font-size:1.4rem;font-weight:900;min-width:20px;text-align:center;}
.tnote{text-align:center;font-size:.74rem;color:var(--text-l);margin-top:7px;}
.tnote b{color:var(--green-d);}
.sdivider{border:none;border-top:1px solid var(--border);margin:16px 0;}

/* ══ 행 선택기 (새 UI) ══ */
.row-selector{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;}
.rs-zone{border-radius:12px;padding:10px 12px;border:2px solid transparent;transition:all .2s;}
.rs-zone.zone1{background:#eef7e4;border-color:var(--green-l);}
.rs-zone.zone2{background:#f0f4ff;border-color:#b8c8f0;}
.rs-zone-label{font-size:.72rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;}
.rs-zone.zone1 .rs-zone-label{color:var(--green-t);}
.rs-zone.zone2 .rs-zone-label{color:#3a5ea8;}
.rs-zone-label .zone-badge{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:50%;font-size:.72rem;font-weight:900;
}
.rs-zone.zone1 .zone-badge{background:var(--green-d);color:#fff;}
.rs-zone.zone2 .zone-badge{background:#3a5ea8;color:#fff;}
.rs-pills{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:7px;min-height:36px;}
.rs-pill{
  padding:7px 16px;border-radius:20px;font-size:.82rem;font-weight:700;
  cursor:pointer;user-select:none;transition:all .15s;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;
  border:2px solid transparent;
}
.rs-pill.p1{background:var(--green-l);color:var(--green-t);border-color:#a8cc88;}
.rs-pill.p1:hover{background:#b0cc98;transform:translateY(-1px);}
.rs-pill.p2{background:#d8e4ff;color:#3a5ea8;border-color:#b0c4f8;}
.rs-pill.p2:hover{background:#c4d4ff;transform:translateY(-1px);}
.rs-pill .pill-arrow{font-size:.7rem;opacity:.6;}
.rs-empty{font-size:.72rem;color:#bbb;padding:6px 0;font-style:italic;}

/* ══ S3: 드래그앤드롭 ══ */
#screen-words.active{display:flex;flex-direction:column;height:100vh;}
#screen-words .dnd-body{flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:14px 16px 10px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;}

/* 상단 현황 바 */
.status-bar{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.sb-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;padding:5px 11px;border-radius:20px;font-size:.78rem;font-weight:700;}
.sb-item.sang{background:var(--red-bg);color:var(--red);}
.sb-item.jung{background:var(--amber-bg);color:var(--amber);}
.sb-item.ha{background:var(--green-bg);color:var(--green);}
.sb-item .sb-num{font-size:1rem;font-weight:900;}
.sb-guide{font-size:.72rem;color:var(--text-l);margin-left:auto;white-space:nowrap;}
.sb-warn{font-size:.72rem;color:#c0392b;font-weight:600;white-space:nowrap;}

/* 칸반 보드 */
.kanban{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:10px;flex:1;min-height:0;}
.kb-col{background:#fff;border-radius:12px;border:2px solid var(--border);display:flex;flex-direction:column;min-height:160px;transition:border-color .2s;}
.kb-col.drag-over{border-color:var(--green-d);background:#f0f7e8;}
.kb-head{padding:10px 12px 8px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-shrink:0;}
.kb-title{font-size:.82rem;font-weight:700;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;}
.kb-count{font-size:.72rem;font-weight:700;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:10px;}
.kb-col.sang-col .kb-title{color:var(--red);}
.kb-col.jung-col .kb-title{color:var(--amber);}
.kb-col.ha-col   .kb-title{color:var(--green);}
.kb-col.sang-col .kb-count{background:var(--red-bg);color:var(--red);}
.kb-col.jung-col .kb-count{background:var(--amber-bg);color:var(--amber);}
.kb-col.ha-col   .kb-count{background:var(--green-bg);color:var(--green);}
.kb-need{font-size:.66rem;color:var(--text-l);}
.kb-cards{flex:1;padding:7px 8px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px;overflow-y:auto;}
.kb-cards::-webkit-scrollbar{width:3px;}
.kb-cards::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:#ddd;border-radius:2px;}
.kb-empty{text-align:center;padding:16px 8px;color:#ccc;font-size:.72rem;}

/* 단어 카드 */
.dcard{background:var(--bg);border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:7px 9px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;cursor:grab;user-select:none;transition:all .15s;}
.dcard:active{cursor:grabbing;}
.dcard.dragging{opacity:.4;transform:scale(.96);}
.dcard.needs{border-color:#f39c12;background:#fffbf0;}
.dc-kr{font-size:.84rem;font-weight:600;}
.dc-jp{font-size:.72rem;color:var(--text-l);font-family:"Noto Sans JP",sans-serif;}
.dc-main{display:flex;flex-direction:row;align-items:center;gap:6px;}
.dc-right{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;}
.dc-db{font-size:.6rem;}
.dc-db.found{color:#27ae60;}
.dc-db.manual{color:#bbb;}
.dc-del{background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;color:#ccc;font-size:.8rem;padding:1px 3px;transition:color .1s;line-height:1;}
.dc-del:hover{color:var(--red);}
.unassigned-col{background:#fffbf0;border-color:#f39c12;}

/* 하단 고정 입력창 */
.bottom-input{background:#fff;border-top:1.5px solid var(--border);padding:12px 16px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;flex-shrink:0;}
.bi-row{display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:stretch;}
.tinput{flex:1;padding:9px 12px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:9px;font-size:.86rem;font-family:inherit;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);transition:border-color .15s;}
.tinput:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--green-d);background:#fff;}
.tinput::placeholder{color:#bbb;}
.bi-bottom{display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:center;}
.upload-zone{flex:1;border:1.5px dashed var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:7px 12px;text-align:center;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;background:var(--bg);font-size:.74rem;color:var(--text-l);}
.upload-zone:hover{border-color:var(--green-d);background:#f0f7e8;color:var(--green-d);}
.hint{font-size:.68rem;color:var(--text-l);}
.word-count-badge{font-size:.72rem;color:var(--text-l);white-space:nowrap;}
.word-count-badge b{color:var(--green-d);}

/* ══ S4: 수행평가 툴 ══ */
#screen-tool{background:#f8faed;height:100vh;overflow:hidden;}
#screen-tool.active{display:flex;flex-direction:column;height:100vh;}
#screen-tool .hdr{flex-shrink:0;}
.tool-body{
  flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;
  justify-content:center;
  padding:2vh 5vw;gap:clamp(6px,2.2vh,22px);
  overflow-y:auto;min-height:0;
}
/* 제목 */
.tool-title-wrap{text-align:center;}
.tool-title{font-size:clamp(1.5rem,4.5vw,5rem);font-weight:900;color:#2d2d2d;display:block;font-family:"Noto Sans KR",sans-serif;line-height:1.15;}
.tool-wavy{
  display:block;width:28vw;height:0;
  border:none;border-top:0.22vw wavy #7ab64a;
  margin:0.8vh auto 0;
}
/* Q 행 */
.q-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1.5vw;}
.q-bookmark{
  width:2.8vw;min-width:2.8vw;flex-shrink:0;
  display:block;
}
.q-bookmark img{
  width:100%;display:block;pointer-events:none;user-select:none;
}
/* Q1 */
.q1-inner{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1vw;flex-wrap:nowrap;}
.q1-label-txt{font-size:2.2vw;font-weight:700;color:#2d2d2d;white-space:nowrap;}
.row-badge{position:relative;width:7.5vw;flex-shrink:0;}
.badge-bg{width:100%;display:block;pointer-events:none;user-select:none;}
.badge-text{
  position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;
  transform:translate(-50%,-50%);
  font-size:1.5vw;font-weight:900;color:#2d5a1a;
  text-align:center;line-height:1.2;white-space:nowrap;
}
.q1-suffix{font-size:2.2vw;font-weight:700;color:#2d2d2d;white-space:nowrap;}
/* Q2 */
.q2-text{font-size:2.4vw;font-weight:700;color:#2d2d2d;}
/* 단어 카드 */
.words-row{
  display:flex;gap:2vw;
  padding-left:4.3vw;
}
.word-card-wrap{
  flex:1;min-width:0;
  display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:0.5vh;
}
.word-num{
  width:2.2vw;height:2.2vw;min-width:2.2vw;
  background:#5a5a5a;color:#fff;border-radius:50%;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  font-size:1.1vw;font-weight:700;
}
.word-card{position:relative;width:100%;}
.card-bg{width:100%;display:block;pointer-events:none;user-select:none;mix-blend-mode:multiply;}
.card-text{
  position:absolute;top:54%;left:50%;
  transform:translate(-50%,-50%);
  font-size:2vw;font-weight:700;
  color:#2d5a1a;text-align:center;white-space:nowrap;
}
/* Click Here 버튼 */
.click-here-btn{
  align-self:center;
  padding:0.9vh 4vw;border:none;border-radius:1.2vw;
  background:#c8ddb0;color:#3a6820;
  font-size:1.7vw;font-weight:700;font-family:inherit;
  cursor:pointer;box-shadow:2px 3px 0 #8fa870;
  transition:background .15s;
}
.click-here-btn:hover{background:#b0cc98;}


/* ══ 반응형 ══ */
/* 태블릿 (768~1200px) */
@media(max-width:1200px){
  .hdr{padding:0 12px;gap:7px;}
  .tool-title{font-size:clamp(1.4rem,5vw,3.8rem);}
  .q-bookmark{width:clamp(24px,2.8vw,42px);}
  .q1-label-txt,.q1-suffix{font-size:clamp(0.9rem,2.2vw,1.8rem);}
  .q1-inner{gap:clamp(4px,0.8vw,12px);}
  .row-badge{width:clamp(55px,7.5vw,90px);}
  .badge-text{font-size:clamp(0.6rem,1.3vw,1.3rem);}
  .q2-text{font-size:clamp(0.9rem,2.4vw,1.9rem);}
  .word-num{width:clamp(18px,2.2vw,32px);height:clamp(18px,2.2vw,32px);min-width:clamp(18px,2.2vw,32px);font-size:clamp(0.6rem,1vw,0.95rem);}
  .card-text{font-size:clamp(0.85rem,2vw,1.7rem);}
  .click-here-btn{font-size:clamp(0.85rem,1.5vw,1.4rem);}
}

/* 모바일/핸드폰 (≤768px) */
@media(max-width:768px){
  /* 헤더 반응형 */
  .hdr{padding:0 10px;gap:6px;}
  .hdr .brand{font-size:0.9rem;}
  .hdr .step{display:none;}
  /* 헤더 내 버튼 (inline style 덮어쓰기) */
  .hdr .btn{font-size:.68rem !important;padding:4px 8px !important;}

  #screen-tool.active{height:auto;min-height:100svh;}
  .tool-body{padding:12px 16px;gap:10px;justify-content:flex-start;overflow-y:auto;}
  .tool-title{font-size:clamp(1.3rem,6vw,2.4rem);}
  .tool-wavy{width:55vw;border-top-width:2px;margin-top:4px;}
  .q-row{gap:8px;}
  .q-bookmark{width:28px;}
  .q1-inner{flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px 8px;}
  .q1-label-txt,.q1-suffix{font-size:0.92rem;}
  .q1-inner .q1-suffix{flex-basis:100%;padding-left:36px;}
  .row-badge{width:52px;}
  .badge-text{font-size:0.65rem;}
  .q2-text{font-size:0.92rem;}
  .words-row{
    display:grid !important;
    grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr !important;
    gap:8px !important;
    padding-left:0 !important;
  }
  .word-card-wrap{flex:unset !important;}
  .word-num{width:22px;height:22px;min-width:22px;font-size:0.65rem;}
  .card-text{font-size:0.85rem;}
  .click-here-btn{font-size:0.92rem;padding:8px 14px;border-radius:10px;align-self:center;}
}

/* 소형 폰 (≤480px) */
@media(max-width:480px){
  .hdr{padding:0 8px;gap:4px;}
  .hdr .brand{display:none;}
  .hdr .btn{font-size:.62rem !important;padding:3px 7px !important;}
  .tool-title{font-size:1.3rem;}
  .words-row{grid-template-columns:1fr !important;}
}

.save-banner{
  background:#fff;border-radius:14px;box-shadow:var(--sh);
  padding:16px 20px;width:100%;max-width:420px;
  border:2px solid var(--green-l);
}
.save-banner-title{font-size:.72rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--text-l);letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;}
.save-info{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;margin-bottom:12px;}
.save-info-row{font-size:.83rem;color:var(--text);display:flex;gap:6px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.save-info-row b{color:var(--green-t);}
.sbadge{display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:10px;font-size:.72rem;font-weight:700;background:var(--green-l);color:var(--green-t);margin-right:2px;}
.save-btn-row{display:flex;gap:8px;}
.btn-load{flex:1;background:var(--green-d);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:9px;padding:10px;font-size:.86rem;font-weight:700;font-family:inherit;cursor:pointer;transition:background .15s;}
.btn-load:hover{background:var(--green-t);}
.btn-clear-save{background:#fff;color:var(--text-l);border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:9px;padding:10px 14px;font-size:.82rem;font-weight:600;font-family:inherit;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;}
.btn-clear-save:hover{border-color:#c0392b;color:#c0392b;}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ══ S1: 문자 선택 ══ -->
<div id="screen-select" class="screen active">
  <div class="hdr">
    <span class="brand">일본어 문자 쓰기 수행평가 툴</span>
    <span class="step">문자 선택</span>
  </div>
  <div class="cwrap">
    <div class="hero">
      <h1>일본어 문자 쓰기 수행평가 툴</h1>
      <p>2022 개정 교육과정 어휘 DB 내장 · 히라가나 / 가타카나</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 저장된 설정 배너 (저장 있을 때만 표시) -->
    <div class="save-banner" id="save-banner" style="display:none;">
      <div class="save-banner-title">💾 저장된 설정</div>
      <div class="save-info" id="save-info-area"></div>
      <div class="save-btn-row">
        <button class="btn-load" onclick="loadSavedState()">▶ 이어서 시작</button>
        <button class="btn-clear-save" onclick="clearSavedState()">삭제</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="script-grid">
      <button class="script-btn" onclick="selectScript('hiragana')">
        <span class="kana">あ</span>
        <span class="lbl">히라가나</span>
        <span class="sub">あいうえお</span>
      </button>
